CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 2, 1957, page 19, reads: "Special Guests... at the NAACP Human Rights dinner were, seated, left to right: Mrs. Robert L. Vann, Atty. Henry Smith, Irving Beauford, Matthew Moore, Mrs. Florence J. Reizenstein and Sylvester Anderson. Standing in same order: Louis Mason Jr., Theodore Jones and Clarence (Larry) Huff. -'Teenie' Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait including, from left to right, Theodore Jones, Jessie Vann, Atty. Henry Smith, Irving Beauford, Matthew Moore, Florence Reizenstein, and Sylvester Anderson, gathered around banquet table for the NAACP Human Rights dinner at the Penn Sheraton Hotel
